| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1782 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4f9e9b9e-829d-5faa-a2d8-edcb3edd3e53"
